Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.86,0:00:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房间的亮度足够了?\N真的?真的是真的?......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要真的照明充足之后再看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.96,0:00:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.47,0:00:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她哭了吧...\N一定是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.48,0:00:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被骂了也还是\N好喜欢好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一副臭脸\N也依然是那么迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.59,0:01:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.49,0:01:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧\N一起来吧 一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来 一起来\N一起来 一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.83,0:01:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一．起．来．吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.44,0:01:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那天以来的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.14,0:01:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论何时都希望能感觉的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.65,0:01:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管到哪里都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.66,0:01:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管做什么都好让人心动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷入恋爱的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.96,0:01:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都好像魔法师一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.87,0:01:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以让人高兴起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能在一起就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.58,0:01:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被骂了也还是\N好喜欢好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一副臭脸\N也依然是那么迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.58,0:02:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.59,0:02:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧 一起来吧\N一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧\N一起来吧 一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来 一起来 一起来\N一起来 一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.63,0:02:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.13,0:02:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初体验!我拥抱了他!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?老妈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.85,0:02:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这万人迷的孩子真是帮了我大忙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.48,0:02:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶，那是谁在做早饭啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.19,0:02:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，怎么了，老公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃，再来是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，二号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.87,0:02:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她说为了你啊\N以后每天都会来家里做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的帮了我不少忙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要做~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.81,0:03:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑!这太奇怪了吧?\N又不是一家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.72,0:03:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，是一家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.62,0:03:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然跟我长的一点也不像\N但是她的的确确是我的家人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.39,0:03:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就是我的亲生女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以那孩子才会\N从早上就待在这儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相大白真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是，太好了太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~好厉害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.74,0:03:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许哪一天她把眼镜拿下来后\N又会给大家添麻烦也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是她究竟是我可爱的独生女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.75,0:03:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了平常能方便照顾她\N最好的方法就是安置在我身边!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.32,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以从今天起\N就把我们家搬到隔壁来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为如此，请各位多多指教了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什么星座啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,双子座，你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别那么和睦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，这样不是反而\N变的更危险吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.68,0:04:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来，真叫人羡慕啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来，快来吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们还吃的下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,井端老师似乎由于\N身体不适请假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.86,0:04:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这段时间\N大家就为期末考做充分的准备吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶，昨天还那么有精神的说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.63,0:04:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菜搞老师她最自豪的\N就是至今从来没有请过假呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.72,0:04:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯~今天的书就看到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起回去吧，老公...嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃，等岩城小弟一出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.73,0:05:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先叫他“岩城小弟!”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后再“真巧呢，在这里遇见你”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.77,0:05:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后再“反正我们就住隔壁\N要不要一起回去啊?”这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.28,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚那个\N好像是岩城小弟...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?二老婆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真巧呢，在这里遇见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.75,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我们就住隔壁\N一起回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公他自己先回去了，你说过不过份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那刚刚那个果然是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最讨厌你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚饭已经做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边也完成了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，老公呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚是叫过了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，那我...\N我去带他下来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.36,0:06:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然，要是不拿出勇气的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢着，响子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.43,0:06:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个样子就已经十分有魅力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样努力去分胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拿下来\N只能在真的，真的有困难的时候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在做什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么，别进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.85,0:07:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃饭罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么...\N我也有做的说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊~可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(老师 不管发生什么事\N打起精神来吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城他终于要做最后的胜负了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后的胜负?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.48,0:07:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁着老师生病心情低落的时候\N一口气向她求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么做又如何呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就糟了啊!\N没有比这更糟的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老师搞不好会\N接受岩城的追求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后抛弃莉采儿\N两人一起私奔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么那样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，你一定要跟紧岩城才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论发生什么事\N都不能离开他喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.63,0:07:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就交给干爹们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干爹谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已进入指定空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再过七秒后投下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.43,0:08:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从德国送来的\N绝对绝对无法被破坏的附锁项圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轻轻的轻轻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.81,0:08:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公还没起床吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿! 咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是老公啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.05,0:08:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了经由地下管道与那些通过领空\N的国家取得协助花去太多时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.83,0:08:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能借点时间?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.84,0:09:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有东西想给老师看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.81,0:09:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你并没有生病吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.71,0:09:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我来就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等、等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶!真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.99,0:09:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.32,0:09:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙还没来...\N老师也是一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.36,0:09:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶!那，是私奔了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去追他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，你不是最喜欢岩城了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然喜欢的话，怎么可以不去追呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.50,0:09:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙可能会去的地方不多\N应该不难找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不去学校了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底要去哪啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里景色好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.03,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从我小时候，只要遇到不顺心的事情\N就会到这儿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是跟谁吵架的时候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然被你看见了啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那花也是岩城同学放的吧\N谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是探病罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然让跟自己订婚的女人哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.77,0:10:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.27,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他根本就不了解老师嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.67,0:10:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是了解的话\N才做不出那种事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很差劲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以叫出来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.18,0:10:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就说“你这种人最差劲了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔、喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.19,0:11:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这种人最差劲了~!\N你这家伙太差劲了~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.96,0:11:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像...感觉很不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.83,0:11:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好...该不会...\N真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.97,0:11:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你，岩城同学\N感觉轻松多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.61,0:11:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样从明天起又可以\N从头来过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.48,0:11:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么说呢\N我跟他彼此的精神状态都很糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.72,0:11:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，托岩城同学的福\N才一天我就恢复了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.62,0:11:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,单纯的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成大人以后啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为想了解对方\N有时也是会哭出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩城同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天真的谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.98,0:12:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛...\N混帐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.02,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到老公了...咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.54,0:12:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会永远跟你在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛啊，莉采儿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没胸部就是没胸部啦，白痴...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.51,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这么说嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.93,0:12:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊\N冲啊 冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊\N冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊 冲啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.31,0:13:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.42,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人和女人真是难以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了查清楚我去了图书馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然对比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.69,0:13:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公是一点兴趣也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.07,0:13:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家好喜欢他，所以我不会哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.74,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不气馁，不逃避，更不会失去勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.95,0:13:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信总有一天春天会到来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.75,0:13:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿出认真的力量，认真的力量向前冲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.46,0:13:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊\N冲啊 冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.86,0:14:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊\N冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.27,0:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊 冲啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公~ 咦?不在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，真是好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.88,0:14:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶，新婚生活吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都感觉很新鲜呢
